The paper deals with few-shot learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The use of domain adaptation techniques to address the domain shift problem in few-shot learning suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), or multimedia (cs.MM). However, since the paper focuses on image classification tasks, it is more likely to belong to the sub-categories of computer vision (cs.CV) or machine learning (cs.LG).
